{"tid":767630,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)詭屋驚凶實錄2 水銀蒸發令","createTime":"2018-08-04T16:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T20:18:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6121eb2973588be83b571eb93585f677af3df8","tid":767630,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=y9yaBAkfFwqnobs0iwLzUNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4ab0620e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=y9yaBAkfFwqnobs0iwLzUNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=dc8f2f97\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=y9yaBAkfFwqnobs0iwLzUNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b1b4340a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg&h=7175e393&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a8/Mercuryrisingposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa8%2FMercuryrisingposter.jpg&h=baba1724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1976年，超自然現象探究者艾德與蘿琳&middot;華倫夫婦辦理了「阿米蒂維爾凶宅事件」，協助堪稱屋子裏發生了多起靈異事件的盧茲一家，來確認該屋子是否在兩年前發生了一場慘烈的血洗事件：一個名叫小羅納德&middot;迪菲歐殘忍在屋子裏殺光了他的家人後，在法庭上稱自己遭魔鬼附身而被迫殺死家人，最後沒被法官採信而被判處連續六個終身監禁。蘿琳運用自己與生俱來的陰陽眼來探查屋子各處時<br />\n<br />\n2.FBI調查員艾特&middot;傑菲（布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）一次奉派調查一起父母離奇遇害，男孩失蹤的案子，當傑菲前往現場查案時，發現這名有自閉症狀的男孩賽門因為父母被殺害而驚嚇過度，無法言語，他歷經的痛苦引起傑菲的共鳴，而且直覺認為他身陷極大危險，於是要求警方為他提供保護。當警方無故撒退，傑菲就帶著賽門逃命<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=y9yaBAkfFwqnobs0iwLzUNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=af612f02\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=y9yaBAkfFwqnobs0iwLzUNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=195855bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70879a874ed39613125400da2e7ce3fbe7570a98","tid":767630,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6c7956f52c6a2ed7245cc3bd3c1c332b704b65","tid":767630,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"幾時播水銀 到時先睇"},{"pid":"c3707a708723578cae03122823fa1736a57d0320","ti